fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">24.2k</span></span></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.joinmastodon.org/\">Documentation &#x26; official explaination</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.joinmastodon.org/client/intro/\">API documentation</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"clients\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#clients\" aria-label=\"clients permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Clients</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.keylesspalace.tusky\">Tusky</a> - Android client.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://f-droid.org/packages/org.mariotaku.twidere/\">Twidere</a> - Android app for Twitter, GNU Social and Mastodon.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/n1k0/tooty\">Tooty</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/n1k0/tooty\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">124</span></span></a> - Experimental multi-account Mastodon Web client (Elm).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ihabunek/toot\">toot</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ihabunek/toot\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">462</span></span></a> - Mastodon CLI client (Python).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/McKael/madonctl\">madonctl</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/McKael/madonctl\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">131</span></span></a> - Mastodon CLI client (Go).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/naumanni/naumanni\">naumanni</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/naumanni/naumanni\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">95</span></span></a> - Web user interface specially designed for Mastodon.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/dysk0/harbour-tooter\">Tooter</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dysk0/harbour-tooter\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">17</span></span></a> - Native client for SailfishOS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://framagit.org/tom79/fedilab\">Fedilab</a> - Android client.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/nolanlawson/pinafore\">Pinafore</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/nolanlawson/pinafore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">564</span></span></a> - Alternative web client for Mastodon, focused on speed and simplicity.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/bleakgrey/tootle\">Tootle</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/bleakgrey/tootle\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">314</span></span></a> - Simple Mastodon client designed for elementary OS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://git.carcosa.net/jmcbray/brutaldon\">Brutaldon</a> - Brutaldon is a brutalist, Web 1.0 web interface for Mastodon.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://notabug.org/halcyon-suite/halcyon\">Halcyon</a> - Alternative web client for Mastodon and Pleroma with a Twitter-like interface.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://whalebird.social/en/desktop/contents\">Whalebird</a> - Electron-based Mastodon client.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://git.mulligrubs.me/planiverse/\">Planiverse</a> - Minimalist, no-JS Web client for Mastodon.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/toot/id1229021451\">Toot!</a> - Mastodon client for iOS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://nicolasconstant.github.io/sengi/\">Sengi</a> - Desktop oriented webapp for Mastodon and Pleroma, focused on multi-accounts usages.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"federated-servers\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#federated-servers\" aria-label=\"federated servers permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Federated servers</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://joinmastodon.org/\">Mastodon</a> - Most known microblogging platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pleroma.social/\">Pleroma</a> - Lightweight microblogging platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gnu.io/social/\">GnuSocial</a> - Oldest microblogging platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://microblog.pub/\">Microblog.pub</a> - Single-user lightweight microblogging platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://zotlabs.org/page/hubzilla/hubzilla-project\">Hubzilla</a> - Blog/social networks platform with file, contacts and events sharing.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://friendi.ca/\">Friendica</a> - Social network platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://joinpeertube.org/\">Peertube</a> - Video sharing platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://funkwhale.audio/\">FunkWhale</a> - Audio sharing platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://joinplu.me/\">Plume</a> - Blogging platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://writefreely.org/\">WriteFreely</a> - Blogging platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/prismosuite/prismo\">Prismo</a> - Link aggregation platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://pixelfed.org/\">PixelFed</a> - Photograph sharing platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://apps.nextcloud.com/apps/social\">NextCloud Social</a> - Microblogging inside the cloud platform.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tools\" aria-label=\"tools permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tools</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://instances.social/list\">Mastodon instances</a> - List of Mastodon instances.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.unmung.com/mastoview\">unmung.com/mastoview</a> - Preview the local or federated timeline of any instance.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://scheduler.mastodon.tools/\">Toot scheduler</a> - Schedule now, toot later.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://framagit.org/luc/last\">Last</a> - Aggregate toots on a web page providing Atom feed and an epub (Perl).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://forget.codl.fr/about/\">Forget</a> - Delete toots after a user defined period of time (Python <a href=\"https://github.com/codl/forget/\">source code</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/codl/forget/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">109</span></span></a>).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://rknightuk.github.io/mastodon-toot-bookmarklet/\">Mastodon Toot Bookmarklet</a> - Bookmarklet to toot the current page (<a href=\"https://github.com/rknightuk/mastodon-toot-bookmarklet/\">source code</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/rknightuk/mastodon-toot-bookmarklet/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">12</span></span></a>)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/addon/mastodon-simplified-federation/\">Mastodon – Simplified Federation!</a> - Redirect clicks on remote follow/interaction buttons to your own instance (<a href=\"https://github.com/rugk/mastodon-simplified-federation\">source code</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/rugk/mastodon-simplified-federation\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">38</span></span></a>).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://fediverse.0qz.fun/\">Fediverse Explorer</a> - Trending hashtags and popular toots, regenerated every hour.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://nowplaying.resynth1943.net\">Mastodon #nowplaying Toot Bookmarklet</a> - Bookmarklet to toot the music you're currently listening to. Works with YouTube. (<a href=\"https://github.com/resynth1943/mastodon-nowplaying-toot-bookmarklet\">source code</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/resynth1943/mastodon-nowplaying-toot-bookmarklet\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">0</span></span></a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"user-styles\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#user-styles\" aria-label=\"user styles permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>User styles</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://userstyles.org/styles/139721/mastodon-glitch-soc-variable-width\">Variable width</a> - Makes Mastodon scale with the browser's width.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://userstyles.org/styles/141457/mastodon-dynamic-wide-columns-narrow-drawer\">Narrow drawer</a> - With the variable width style, makes the drawer narrower and the other columns scale accordingly.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"user-scripts\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#user-scripts\" aria-label=\"user scripts permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>User scripts</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://greasyfork.org/fr/scripts/29228-mastodon-nsfw-remover\">NSFW Remover</a> - Automatically display NSFW images.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://openuserjs.org/scripts/bl00m/Mastodon_Customizable_Interface\">Customizable interface</a> - Move and resize columns on a grid.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/pmorinerie/birdsite\">BirdSite</a> - Browser extension for cross-posting Mastodon toots to Twitter.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"bots\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bots\" aria-label=\"bots permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Bots</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/chaica/feed2toot\">feed2toot</a> - Automatically parses RSS feeds, identifies new posts and posts them on Mastodon (Python).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/josefkenny/usercount\">usercount</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/josefkenny/usercount\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">45</span></span></a> - Bot which posts user statistics to Mastodon (Python).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/gled-rs/mastodon-autofollow\">autofollow</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/gled-rs/mastodon-autofollow\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">29</span></span></a> - Autofollow bot for Mastodon (Python).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/raymestalez/mastodon-hnbot\">hnbot</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/raymestalez/mastodon-hnbot\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">38</span></span></a> - Posts the Hacker News stories with 100+ points (Python).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://christopher.su/projects/translator/\">translator</a> - Translate any toot into the desired language using <code class=\"language-text\">@translator@toot.works [langcode]</code>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mastodon.social/@TrendingBot\">@TrendingBot@mastodon.social</a> - Shows you what's trending on Mastodon.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/chaica/remindr\">Remindr</a> - Automatically send reminders to both Mastodon and Twitter from a list of resources (Python).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://botsin.space/@newsbot\">News Bot</a> - mirrors Twitter accounts on Mastodon (ClojureScript), source available on <a href=\"https://github.com/yogthos/mastodon-bot\">GitHub</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/yogthos/mastodon-bot\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">160</span></span></a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/indyhall/mastodon-welcome-bot\">Welcome Bot</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/indyhall/mastodon-welcome-bot\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">5</span></span></a> - Automatically send a welcome DM to new users (Python).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"news--magazines-bots\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#news--magazines-bots\" aria-label=\"news  magazines bots permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>News &#x26; magazines bots</h2>\n<p>Please note: most of them are non-official. Also, we do not <em>recommend</em> any, they are just listed here for your information.</p>\n<h3 id=\"english\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#english\" aria-label=\"english permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1